WEBVTT

00:27.060 --> 00:30.220
Don't I look like a beautiful picture?

00:31.340 --> 00:33.280
Always.

00:33.670 --> 00:36.080
I finished all the paperwork. We can go now.

00:36.080 --> 00:37.460
I'll wheel you to the car.

00:37.460 --> 00:38.590
I'll be your girlfriend today,

00:38.590 --> 00:40.010
not your doctor.

00:40.300 --> 00:41.870
Really?

00:41.870 --> 00:43.250
I'm so excited.

00:43.250 --> 00:44.670
Let's go!

00:46.300 --> 00:48.100
The weather's nice.

00:48.940 --> 00:50.830
The clouds were so beautiful in Uruk.

00:51.530 --> 00:53.450
Do you want to go back there with me?

00:53.450 --> 00:54.850
With you?

00:54.850 --> 00:56.890
Why? Do you want to go with someone else?

00:56.890 --> 00:58.480
It's possible.

00:59.960 --> 01:01.310
What were you listening to?

01:02.380 --> 01:03.690
This is my favorite.

01:03.690 --> 01:05.090
Do you want to listen to it?

01:14.570 --> 01:16.830
If I'd known I'd die like this,

01:17.230 --> 01:21.830
I would've told you how I felt about you.

01:21.870 --> 01:22.460
Hey!

01:24.320 --> 01:27.789
Dr. Kang! Dr. Kang!

01:27.789 --> 01:30.060
Please! Hey! Hey! Hey!

01:37.210 --> 01:37.979
Are you okay?

01:37.979 --> 01:38.850
Oh my! Oh my!

01:38.850 --> 01:40.870
I'm okay. I'm quite flexible...

01:41.900 --> 01:44.000
Geeze. This is really expensive.

01:44.000 --> 01:45.520
This is terrible!

01:46.810 --> 01:49.590
Are you worried about the wheelchair now?

01:50.410 --> 01:53.120
I just got out of the hospital 10 minutes and I almost died again.

01:53.120 --> 01:55.840
This was almost attempted murder.

01:55.840 --> 01:58.039
Why were you listening to that?

01:58.650 --> 02:00.450
What should I do with this wheelchair?

02:00.450 --> 02:01.930
You’re getting clumsy.

02:01.930 --> 02:03.470
Do I have to pay for this wheelchair now?

02:03.470 --> 02:06.480
You shouldn't use public transportation.

02:06.480 --> 02:08.160
For the safety of your fellow citizens.

02:08.610 --> 02:09.970
Shut up!

02:27.600 --> 02:28.520
If you have something to say, do it now.

02:28.910 --> 02:30.100
I'm going to leave when I finish eating.

02:31.400 --> 02:32.260
And I've almost finished.

02:32.260 --> 02:33.329
I have nothing to tell you.

02:38.360 --> 02:40.520
Why did you ask me to eat with you if you had nothing to tell me?

02:40.520 --> 02:42.070
Because you're too skinny.

02:46.950 --> 02:48.980
I'm confused now.

02:49.300 --> 02:50.730
What are we?

02:51.180 --> 02:53.670
Have we broken up or just a quarrel between us?

02:53.670 --> 02:55.120
What are we?

02:56.190 --> 02:57.260
Are we going to break up?

02:57.260 --> 02:58.860
Are we in the process of breaking up?

02:59.660 --> 03:00.960
Have we broken up?

03:02.320 --> 03:04.760
I'm on my way to Yoon Myung Joo.

03:04.760 --> 03:06.440
You haven't changed your mind?

03:06.760 --> 03:07.920
Please support my decision.

03:07.920 --> 03:09.280
You're going to retire from the army

03:09.280 --> 03:10.780
and work for my uncle's company

03:10.780 --> 03:12.160
to live as my father's son-in-law?

03:12.160 --> 03:13.300
Will you suffer all of these?

03:13.300 --> 03:14.460
You're going to be with me.

03:14.460 --> 03:16.970
You look so happy.

03:19.570 --> 03:21.040
I'll retire from the army.

03:21.040 --> 03:22.329
I won't see my father again.

03:23.200 --> 03:24.540
He's got his life

03:24.540 --> 03:26.079
and I've got mine.

03:26.590 --> 03:28.079
I can live without seeing my father.

03:28.079 --> 03:29.640
How can you say that?

03:30.810 --> 03:33.160
You'll be promoted to major, lieutenant colonel, colonel

03:33.160 --> 03:34.730
and will

03:34.990 --> 03:36.980
certainly become a general.

03:38.010 --> 03:40.150
You're a talented and persevering doctor.

03:41.460 --> 03:43.079
I wouldn't let you give up your career.

03:46.690 --> 03:48.460
I know what you mean,

03:49.530 --> 03:51.120
but I hate you.

03:51.120 --> 03:52.530
You don't think I hate you now?

03:53.040 --> 03:54.060
Are you done?

03:54.220 --> 03:55.850
I came here to treat you.

03:56.170 --> 03:57.360
Bye.

04:00.820 --> 04:02.660
Next time, I want you to come with your answer.

04:03.490 --> 04:05.330
Whether you'll break up with me or not.

04:32.170 --> 04:33.470
What are you doing?

04:34.310 --> 04:35.710
I'm going to take a shower.

04:39.330 --> 04:40.960
Have you missed me already?

04:40.960 --> 04:42.159
Aren't you taking a shower?

04:42.750 --> 04:44.090
So?

04:44.420 --> 04:46.380
Why are you still wearing clothes?

04:47.220 --> 04:49.260
Is that why you beginning video call?

04:49.260 --> 04:50.920
Not because you missed me?

04:50.920 --> 04:52.050
I miss you all the time,

04:52.050 --> 04:53.070
in all styles.

04:53.070 --> 04:54.330
Pervert!

04:54.330 --> 04:56.170
I'll take them off after I hang up.

04:56.170 --> 04:57.430
Bye.

05:06.010 --> 05:06.870
Why did you lie?

05:06.870 --> 05:08.510
You're still dressed.

05:09.320 --> 05:10.840
You're unbelievable!

05:11.730 --> 05:12.830
What are you doing here?

05:12.830 --> 05:14.010
Did you get off work?

05:14.010 --> 05:15.090
I'm on sick leave.

05:15.750 --> 05:18.080
I came here to get a doctor's note.

05:18.790 --> 05:20.660
You should've gone to the hospital.

05:21.390 --> 05:23.670
I should see my doctor first.

05:25.030 --> 05:26.800
You're still sick. What are these?

05:28.070 --> 05:29.080
Painkillers?

05:29.770 --> 05:32.430
Before I get your note, I want to see something.

05:32.430 --> 05:33.659
Fill the tub with water.

05:33.659 --> 05:34.580
Don't even dream of it.

05:34.580 --> 05:36.100
It's my dream. I'll do whatever I want.

05:38.820 --> 05:39.890
I'll wait. Go take a shower.

05:40.180 --> 05:41.030
Why do you keep asking me to shower?

05:41.030 --> 05:42.670
It's my body. I'll do whatever I want.

05:43.230 --> 05:45.490
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

05:45.640 --> 05:47.820
Don't start without me. I counted them all.

05:55.190 --> 05:57.240
What's this?

05:57.920 --> 05:59.150
My gift to you.

05:59.150 --> 06:00.710
You'll look pretty from every direction.

06:02.580 --> 06:03.780
You're unbelievably pretty.

06:04.450 --> 06:06.160
You didn't know?

06:06.850 --> 06:08.400
How did you know what kind of candle I like?

06:08.400 --> 06:09.500
I'm observant

06:09.500 --> 06:10.540
after seeing them once.

06:10.540 --> 06:12.350
Did you think that I only come here once?

06:13.010 --> 06:14.150
No.

06:14.150 --> 06:15.220
How many times?

06:15.550 --> 06:17.060
Why? I don't want to know.

06:18.500 --> 06:19.850
Put it down.

06:20.590 --> 06:22.380
Right. I remember now.

06:22.380 --> 06:23.100
When I was drunk.

06:23.100 --> 06:23.680
When?

06:23.680 --> 06:24.900
A long time ago.

06:27.150 --> 06:29.530
You're not allowed to drink with other guys.

06:29.530 --> 06:30.710
What if I do?

06:30.710 --> 06:31.950
Will you chase me in a chopper?

06:31.950 --> 06:33.300
You don't think I would?

06:33.900 --> 06:35.080
Right.

06:35.080 --> 06:39.110
When you came to rescue me from Private Ryan.

06:39.110 --> 06:41.380
Why were you on an Arabic chopper?

06:45.480 --> 06:47.570
Ouch! My arm still hurts...

06:47.840 --> 06:49.100
You didn't fall on that side.

06:49.100 --> 06:50.580
I know. I fell on... Ouch.

06:53.540 --> 06:55.340
Tell me honestly.

06:55.340 --> 06:56.490
I won't be mad.

06:57.310 --> 06:58.110
For real?

06:58.110 --> 07:00.330
Tell me you didn't use that name card.

07:02.440 --> 07:03.410
Do you want to make a toast?

07:04.080 --> 07:05.470
Did you use the other card

07:05.470 --> 07:06.370
to hire that chopper?

07:06.370 --> 07:07.340
Don't you think

07:08.110 --> 07:10.340
that's why we're still alive?

07:11.170 --> 07:12.270
I don't care.

07:12.270 --> 07:13.730
The name card is gone.

07:13.730 --> 07:14.960
Tell me honestly.

07:14.960 --> 07:16.690
Was there anything in the chopper?

07:16.690 --> 07:18.690
A deed to a petroleum factory?

07:18.690 --> 07:20.030
-No.
-Cash would be nice.

07:20.030 --> 07:21.940
Bonds are also convenient.

07:21.940 --> 07:23.010
Think about it.

07:23.010 --> 07:24.810
Didn't you find a briefcase in the chopper?

07:24.810 --> 07:28.190
I'm so thirsty. Where's the water? Water?

07:28.190 --> 07:29.200
Stop right there.

07:30.020 --> 07:32.050
How could you use that card

07:32.050 --> 07:33.970
for transportation?

07:33.970 --> 07:35.820
Is it a traffic card?

07:36.170 --> 07:37.700
Give me my card back!

07:39.580 --> 07:41.580
You're so materialistic!

07:43.120 --> 07:44.370
Hey!

07:47.080 --> 07:48.050
Do your best!

07:48.050 --> 07:48.920
I'll try.

07:48.920 --> 07:49.970
I have faith in you.

07:50.350 --> 07:51.320
Ki Bum!

07:51.320 --> 07:52.680
Good luck!

07:54.930 --> 07:56.650
Ki Bum!

07:58.010 --> 07:59.110
What are you doing here?

07:59.970 --> 08:01.930
Are you here to cheer for me?

08:01.930 --> 08:03.810
In person? As a group?

08:04.060 --> 08:05.030
For fun?

08:05.960 --> 08:06.960
Maybe not "for fun."

08:07.220 --> 08:08.330
For fun?

08:09.150 --> 08:11.070
We took our precious time off.

08:11.070 --> 08:13.680
Sergeant Gong, do you think he'd pass?

08:13.680 --> 08:14.960
We know how to help him.

08:15.930 --> 08:17.520
This is good luck candy.

08:17.990 --> 08:19.080
This is a good luck fork.

08:19.500 --> 08:21.440
Eat this candy

08:21.440 --> 08:23.900
and pick the right answer with this fork.

08:27.730 --> 08:29.810
If you don't know the answer, choose number three.

08:29.810 --> 08:30.880
You can do it, right?

08:31.450 --> 08:33.460
Corporal Kim Ki Bum!

08:33.460 --> 08:34.730
I'm serving in the army.

08:34.730 --> 08:36.580
This test is a piece of cake.

08:37.460 --> 08:39.900
I'll definitely be victorious.

08:39.900 --> 08:41.020
Sir!

08:41.510 --> 08:43.450
- Good luck!
- Yes, sir!

08:43.789 --> 08:44.960
- Go Ki Bum!
- Go Ki Bum!

08:44.960 --> 08:46.820
-If you don't know the answer, choose number three.
- Go Ki Bum!

08:46.820 --> 08:48.190
Good luck.

08:51.760 --> 08:53.230
People are staring at us.

08:54.230 --> 08:55.460
Act like civilians.

08:55.460 --> 08:56.890
Civilians.

08:58.180 --> 09:01.550
Don't do that. Geeze.

09:02.900 --> 09:06.060
Learn to act normal in plain clothes.

09:13.260 --> 09:14.220
Sir!

09:19.650 --> 09:21.750
Alpha Team will join a combined operation,

09:21.750 --> 09:23.080
in full winter gear,

09:23.080 --> 09:26.160
gather at Airfield 463 by 21:00 p.m.

09:34.090 --> 09:35.350
Sergeant Seo,

09:35.350 --> 09:36.630
Commander Yoon summoned you.

09:38.550 --> 09:40.350
This is a three-month long operation.

09:41.090 --> 09:43.960
Since I didn't find a replacement for you yet.

09:44.620 --> 09:47.610
I want to send you on this operation.

09:48.240 --> 09:49.620
If not,

09:50.540 --> 09:51.310
I can sign

09:51.310 --> 09:54.260
your retirement form right now.

09:54.260 --> 09:55.210
What's it going to be?

09:56.760 --> 09:58.100
I want to go.

09:59.040 --> 10:03.000
Okay. Then go.

10:03.000 --> 10:06.380
You have my permission.

10:06.380 --> 10:08.140
I will deal with this issue when we have

10:08.140 --> 10:09.670
your replacement, considering the special circumstances of Alpha Team.

10:09.670 --> 10:11.270
Let's leave it at that for now.

10:11.270 --> 10:14.410
I don't know when I can find your replacement.

10:15.750 --> 10:18.790
I'm sorry, but do you mean...

10:18.790 --> 10:20.570
When you come back, visit me with Myung Joo.

10:21.090 --> 10:23.670
I'll treat you

10:24.600 --> 10:26.790
no, you and Myung Joo, to some coffee.

10:26.790 --> 10:27.480
Sir!

10:27.480 --> 10:29.910
You're supposed to be there by 21:00 p.m.

10:30.150 --> 10:33.600
Don't be late and come back in one piece.

10:35.430 --> 10:37.670
Yes, sir!

10:37.670 --> 10:39.430
I'll come back in one piece, sir!

10:39.910 --> 10:41.050
Sir.

10:42.030 --> 10:43.280
Sir.

11:26.060 --> 11:27.160
Ah?

11:28.990 --> 11:29.830
What is it?

11:30.580 --> 11:32.360
Jwadi means "baby goat" in Arabic.

11:32.360 --> 11:33.900
Why does your story have no lead up to it?

11:33.900 --> 11:35.340
What's with the

11:35.340 --> 11:36.860
baby goat?

11:37.660 --> 11:41.280
First, I'm friends with Daniel on social media.

11:41.280 --> 11:44.370
Second, I asked him how Jwadi was doing.

11:44.370 --> 11:46.750
Daniel said "jwadi" means "baby goat."

11:47.420 --> 11:51.280
Third, Jwadi wasn't Blacky's name.

11:51.280 --> 11:53.060
You haven't figured out his name yet?

11:54.300 --> 11:56.690
In conclusion, clench your teeth.

11:57.960 --> 11:58.850
Clench them.

11:58.850 --> 12:01.740
Blacky kept saying "Jwadi this and Jwadi that", so...

12:01.740 --> 12:03.120
Hello?

12:06.250 --> 12:08.420
We're not supposed to meet for another two hours.

12:08.420 --> 12:09.480
You're early,

12:09.480 --> 12:10.600
like last time.

12:15.380 --> 12:16.610
What is it?

12:18.340 --> 12:20.240
You're not early.

12:21.340 --> 12:22.790
No.

12:23.280 --> 12:24.550
Department store again?

12:24.990 --> 12:25.910
Yes.

12:27.620 --> 12:30.170
This is the only time

12:31.650 --> 12:33.320
that I could see you.

12:34.480 --> 12:35.660
I wanted to see you before I left.

12:36.410 --> 12:37.500
How long?

12:37.890 --> 12:39.770
A week? Two weeks?

12:41.710 --> 12:42.540
Three months.

12:43.050 --> 12:44.160
Three months?

12:45.620 --> 12:47.850
Is the department store abroad?

12:50.190 --> 12:51.600
Consider that I've joined the army.

12:52.440 --> 12:53.900
If you join the army,

12:53.900 --> 12:55.410
you get your first leave after 100 days.

12:58.540 --> 12:59.370
Are you making me one

12:59.370 --> 13:00.860
of those girls now?

13:01.200 --> 13:02.570
Don't drink with other guys.

13:09.820 --> 13:11.230
Sorry.

13:11.230 --> 13:12.790
I'm trying not to cry,

13:12.790 --> 13:14.650
but it's hard.

13:20.620 --> 13:23.470
I'm sorry that I'm putting you through this.

13:23.470 --> 13:25.150
Please come back soon.

13:25.640 --> 13:27.610
Don't get hurt.

13:27.610 --> 13:28.860
Don't be late.

13:30.130 --> 13:31.240
I won't get hurt.

13:32.510 --> 13:33.720
I won't die.

13:36.530 --> 13:37.910
I'll come back.

13:37.910 --> 13:39.010
I promise.

13:43.380 --> 13:44.960
Will you be able to call me?

13:46.950 --> 13:49.540
I don't think I can get an Internet connection there.

13:50.020 --> 13:53.730
I'll call you whenever I can, though.

13:56.340 --> 13:58.890
Hang in there for a season.

14:00.280 --> 14:04.570
I'll come back when the seasons change.

14:08.010 --> 14:09.630
Bye.

14:11.280 --> 14:12.440
Already?

14:12.790 --> 14:14.190
Hold on.

14:24.280 --> 14:25.560
I'm going to miss you.

14:27.710 --> 14:29.700
Me too.

15:02.510 --> 15:05.120
Big Boss.

15:07.080 --> 15:08.820
He's smart

15:08.820 --> 15:11.350
funny...

15:12.700 --> 15:14.980
and mysterious.

15:16.680 --> 15:18.200
But

15:18.200 --> 15:21.290
he has a lot of secrets.

15:21.700 --> 15:24.260
He'll disappear from time to time

15:24.460 --> 15:26.540
and be hard to contact.

15:27.470 --> 15:29.560
And then one day...

15:34.050 --> 15:36.810
he'll never come back.

15:41.820 --> 15:42.860
Mo Yeon.

15:43.900 --> 15:45.050
Mo Yeon.

15:46.750 --> 15:48.180
Mo Yeon.

15:48.180 --> 15:49.320
What?

15:49.810 --> 15:50.790
Are you okay?

15:50.790 --> 15:52.330
You've been acting

15:52.330 --> 15:53.330
weird since yesterday.

15:59.520 --> 16:00.990
I got here safely.

16:01.840 --> 16:04.380
I miss you so much.

16:08.790 --> 16:10.110
I'm going to work.

16:10.510 --> 16:12.410
The sky is really high in Seoul.

16:12.410 --> 16:13.710
How is it there?

16:14.080 --> 16:16.030
Is it cold? Is it hot?

16:17.000 --> 16:18.520
Wherever you are,

16:18.520 --> 16:21.520
I miss you a lot.

16:22.090 --> 16:24.170
The national anthem is on TV.

16:24.170 --> 16:25.810
Why am I dating a guy

16:25.810 --> 16:27.720
whose theme song is the national anthem?

16:28.790 --> 16:32.740
As people of the Republic of Korea...

16:32.740 --> 16:35.150
Come back soon.

16:35.150 --> 16:36.600
I miss you.

16:38.920 --> 16:41.550
I'm having a late lunch due to my busy schedule.

16:42.700 --> 16:45.210
It's winter here.

16:45.630 --> 16:47.310
You said you'd come back when the seasons change.

16:47.310 --> 16:48.660
Why you haven’t come back yet?

16:48.960 --> 16:51.240
You haven't sent me a message,

16:51.240 --> 16:53.300
so I'm sad.

17:09.770 --> 17:12.490
I wish you were on that chopper.

17:23.230 --> 17:24.319
You guys go ahead.

17:25.060 --> 17:27.290
Wild Wolf and I will be right behind you.

17:27.290 --> 17:28.420
Yes, sir!

17:28.990 --> 17:30.800
Go! Go!

17:34.450 --> 17:35.630
This is Big Boss.

17:35.630 --> 17:37.540
The chopper Tango-Nine has just taken off

17:37.540 --> 17:39.700
with three civilians we rescued.

17:40.880 --> 17:42.600
We'll be heading home in 10 minutes.

17:42.600 --> 17:43.780
Yes, sir.

17:47.790 --> 17:48.890
Captain!

17:49.860 --> 17:51.120
Captain!

17:51.800 --> 17:53.040
Captain!

17:55.050 --> 17:56.450
Captain!

17:59.210 --> 18:00.260
Captain!

18:52.360 --> 18:53.430
Hop on!

18:53.430 --> 18:54.540
We're going home.

19:00.190 --> 19:02.200
We'll drink soju for three days in a row.

19:04.550 --> 19:05.520
Yes, sir.

19:14.750 --> 19:16.320
I will go.

19:16.810 --> 19:18.280
What are you talking about?

19:18.750 --> 19:20.160
Wake up!

19:20.160 --> 19:21.750
You can't fall asleep now.

19:22.050 --> 19:23.190
Look at me,

19:23.190 --> 19:24.350
Captain Yoo!

19:25.080 --> 19:26.320
You can't fall asleep.

19:26.320 --> 19:28.430
Captain!

19:37.080 --> 19:39.150
Big Boss! Wild Wolf! Can you hear me?

19:40.130 --> 19:41.470
What's going on?

19:42.230 --> 19:44.210
Can someone answer, please?

19:48.170 --> 19:49.870
- Captain!
- Captain!

19:49.870 --> 19:50.580
Captain!

19:50.580 --> 19:55.600
Captain!Captain!

19:56.960 --> 19:58.280
You jerk!

20:17.970 --> 20:19.670
How can you do this to me?

20:19.670 --> 20:20.700
Even if you'd sent me a letter from Mars,

20:20.700 --> 20:23.140
I would've gotten it by now.

20:23.580 --> 20:24.850
I'm going out to drink

20:25.110 --> 20:26.890
with a gorgeous man.

20:27.210 --> 20:28.580
Come and get me.

20:38.180 --> 20:39.530
If he doesn't check your messages,

20:39.530 --> 20:40.570
just assume that

20:40.570 --> 20:42.320
he's got no phone connection.

20:42.370 --> 20:43.820
Why do you keep sending messages

20:43.820 --> 20:45.200
and then get frustrated every time?

20:45.590 --> 20:47.280
I want him to

20:47.280 --> 20:48.320
feel guilty

20:48.320 --> 20:49.510
when he checks his messages later.

20:49.700 --> 20:50.750
Are they usually unreachable

20:50.750 --> 20:51.630
when they're on an operation?

20:51.680 --> 20:52.420
I couldn’t contact with him

20:52.420 --> 20:54.400
whenever I want.

20:54.710 --> 20:55.500
We've been apart for more days

20:55.500 --> 20:57.140
than we've been together.

20:57.900 --> 20:58.940
Did you two make up

20:58.940 --> 21:00.490
before he left?

21:01.410 --> 21:02.660
No.

21:03.310 --> 21:05.510
This isn't a lovers' quarrel. This is war.

21:05.690 --> 21:07.880
I can't lose this one.

21:08.770 --> 21:10.300
He left his dog tags with me

21:10.300 --> 21:12.690
so I think that I have the upper hand.

21:13.190 --> 21:14.150
Cheers!

21:15.220 --> 21:16.190
Cheers!

21:17.060 --> 21:18.140
As soon as he gets back,

21:18.140 --> 21:20.230
I don't care how busy the hospital is.

21:20.270 --> 21:22.050
I'm going to confiscate his phone and go on a trip

21:22.050 --> 21:24.380
for a whole week.

21:24.650 --> 21:26.050
I'll get a hotel room

21:26.050 --> 21:26.990
in a remote place,

21:26.990 --> 21:28.120
lock him up in the room, and fight.

21:35.430 --> 21:36.480
Wow!

21:36.830 --> 21:37.650
Did you get a reply?

21:37.650 --> 21:39.590
Private Kim won a soccer game and got some time off.

21:39.590 --> 21:42.100
I'm a member of "Soldiers' Girlfriends."

21:42.600 --> 21:47.400
Congratulations, Hye Gyeong Solgirl.

21:47.970 --> 21:48.850
You're hilarious!

21:50.960 --> 21:53.790
Pour me another one, Mo Yeon Solgirl.

21:54.220 --> 21:56.650
Wow! You're a heavy drinker.

22:02.080 --> 22:03.090
Huh? It's raining.

22:05.050 --> 22:06.480
It's been raining for quite some time.

22:11.170 --> 22:14.740
I wish those two were with us right now.

22:18.010 --> 22:19.570
They'll come back soon.

22:21.050 --> 22:22.080
Right?

22:23.260 --> 22:24.660
They'll come back soon.

22:47.310 --> 22:48.520
Attention!

22:50.490 --> 22:52.700
Salute the commander!

22:52.700 --> 22:54.080
Sir!

22:59.480 --> 23:01.520
At ease!

23:02.320 --> 23:04.070
We've finished our search mission.

23:04.920 --> 23:06.370
The bodies...

23:10.840 --> 23:13.180
We couldn't find the bodies.

24:48.040 --> 24:49.610
Sergeant Kim Beom Rae!

24:50.770 --> 24:51.760
What is it?

24:53.450 --> 24:55.800
Sergeant Kim Beom Rae!

24:55.800 --> 24:57.170
Tell me. What is it?

25:00.460 --> 25:01.910
Sergeant Seo's back!

25:03.610 --> 25:04.740
I'll be right there.

25:06.840 --> 25:07.920
Tell him not to go anywhere.

25:11.540 --> 25:13.290
I have something...

25:14.810 --> 25:18.860
to report to you.

25:20.050 --> 25:21.210
Sergeant Choi?

25:21.790 --> 25:23.520
Hello.

25:23.520 --> 25:24.390
I saw the car

25:24.390 --> 25:25.830
and thought Captain Yoo was here.

25:25.830 --> 25:28.040
What are you doing here?

25:34.250 --> 25:35.730
I'm so

25:39.360 --> 25:41.170
sorry.

25:42.080 --> 25:43.550
What are you sorry about?

25:43.550 --> 25:45.630
Captain Yoo Shi Jin

25:46.290 --> 25:48.430
and Sergeant Seo Dae Young

25:49.850 --> 25:52.510
from the Special

25:53.560 --> 25:55.910
Warfare Command...

25:58.350 --> 25:59.750
were killed while carrying out an operation.

26:02.160 --> 26:03.530
What?

26:04.100 --> 26:05.970
What kind of report is this?

26:09.010 --> 26:11.290
I don't understand what you just said.

26:11.290 --> 26:15.090
Oh my!

26:19.550 --> 26:21.270
Can't you do it right?

26:23.180 --> 26:25.810
Do it like you usually do.

26:28.490 --> 26:30.260
Say it again.

26:33.140 --> 26:35.020
Say it again!

26:57.250 --> 27:00.530
We write our wills before going on an operation.

27:02.290 --> 27:06.420
I hope you don't have to read this letter

27:07.240 --> 27:09.100
but if there's a one in a million chance,

27:09.100 --> 27:12.130
you're reading it now.

27:12.890 --> 27:14.950
I guess I couldn't keep my promises.

27:17.150 --> 27:19.200
I told you not to worry.

27:19.840 --> 27:22.440
I said I wouldn't get injured.

27:22.640 --> 27:24.670
I promised that I wouldn't die.

27:25.370 --> 27:28.420
I promised that I'd come back for sure.

27:28.990 --> 27:31.540
I didn't keep any of those promises.

27:32.600 --> 27:33.770
I'm sorry.

27:36.340 --> 27:40.330
Wherever you were, that place was bright.

27:44.960 --> 27:47.060
I met you

27:48.630 --> 27:50.640
and I loved you.

27:51.660 --> 27:54.010
Now I have to leave you behind like this.

27:55.230 --> 27:56.980
I'm so sorry.

28:25.880 --> 28:27.280
This isn't true.

28:30.260 --> 28:32.290
It can't be.

28:34.950 --> 28:37.000
Tell me it's not true.

28:37.000 --> 28:38.120
I'm sorry.

28:38.850 --> 28:40.160
Dad, please.

28:42.520 --> 28:44.340
Please.

28:46.290 --> 28:48.080
Tell me it's not true.

28:48.080 --> 28:49.510
It's not true.

28:58.320 --> 29:00.310
This is

29:01.360 --> 29:03.570
from Seo Dae Young to you.

29:05.180 --> 29:06.600
No!

29:07.520 --> 29:08.830
Don't!

29:11.440 --> 29:13.010
I don't want it.

29:14.680 --> 29:16.170
If I read it...

29:17.980 --> 29:19.530
if I accept it...

29:21.790 --> 29:24.340
He's really dead.

29:29.760 --> 29:31.520
This is all your fault.

29:32.210 --> 29:33.460
You took all the time that

29:33.460 --> 29:35.250
we could have been happy together away.

29:37.150 --> 29:39.870
I haven't even make up with him yet.

29:39.870 --> 29:42.780
I said nasty things to him before he left.

29:44.410 --> 29:46.370
These are the last words

29:46.710 --> 29:48.420
of an honorable soldier.

29:50.110 --> 29:52.040
Keep it.

29:53.450 --> 29:55.340
No.

29:55.930 --> 29:57.720
I said no!

30:25.890 --> 30:27.510
What are you doing here?

30:28.850 --> 30:30.470
Why are you crying?

30:31.490 --> 30:33.960
If you cry like this, what should I do?

30:37.000 --> 30:39.520
I can't ask you anything.

30:39.520 --> 30:42.250
Do you know how I dragged myself here?

30:42.780 --> 30:44.070
If you're crying,

30:44.070 --> 30:45.260
what am I supposed to do?

30:47.820 --> 30:49.660
Your father is up there, right?

30:49.990 --> 30:51.570
Did he check everything?

30:51.570 --> 30:53.200
This might be incorrect information.

30:53.200 --> 30:55.060
It might be an anomaly.

30:55.060 --> 30:56.860
Have you checked everything?

30:59.100 --> 30:59.750
Stop crying

30:59.750 --> 31:02.070
and answer me, Yoon Myung Joo!

31:14.240 --> 31:17.070
Is this real?

31:21.110 --> 31:23.440
They're not coming back?

31:23.960 --> 31:27.890
I can't see him anymore?

31:30.450 --> 31:34.160
He's not coming back?

32:22.570 --> 32:24.420
I'm sorry to say this

32:24.420 --> 32:27.480
but I hope you don't cry too long because of me.

32:28.600 --> 32:33.300
I want you to shine brightly

32:33.840 --> 32:38.710
and not remember me for too long.

32:40.710 --> 32:42.730
That's what I want.

32:50.330 --> 32:51.990
The army will make an official announcement

32:51.990 --> 32:54.430
a week from now.

32:56.160 --> 32:59.720
Officially, Captain Yoo and Sergeant Seo

33:00.670 --> 33:03.650
died in a car accident while training.

33:10.840 --> 33:12.220
For security regulations,

33:13.270 --> 33:15.900
you have to sign this confidentiality agreement.

33:17.140 --> 33:19.230
Please cooperate.

33:25.850 --> 33:27.900
Did his death

33:29.810 --> 33:32.710
save other lives?

33:32.860 --> 33:35.130
Yes, it did.

33:41.250 --> 33:43.290
Did his death keep peace

33:44.750 --> 33:48.990
in a certain area?

33:51.910 --> 33:53.890
Yes, it did.

33:54.360 --> 33:56.290
Did his death

33:57.900 --> 34:00.270
benefit his country?

34:01.350 --> 34:02.530
Yes,

34:04.110 --> 34:05.300
it did.

34:05.300 --> 34:07.850
But still his country is

34:09.420 --> 34:13.630
making me sign this paper.

34:16.420 --> 34:17.880
I'm sorry.

34:21.750 --> 34:24.840
What's wrong with you?

34:25.780 --> 34:31.219
Why did you choose a life like this?

34:31.870 --> 34:35.670
How come your death has to be confidential?

34:39.409 --> 34:41.750
I hope what I'm doing now

34:45.530 --> 34:47.710
is what you'd want me to do,

34:49.440 --> 34:51.000
Captain Yoo Shi Jin.

36:02.180 --> 36:03.170
I heard you shaved eight minutes off your time

36:03.170 --> 36:04.890
and reclaimed your title?

36:04.890 --> 36:05.840
I'm proud of you.

36:06.520 --> 36:07.800
As your friend,

36:07.800 --> 36:11.370
Congratulations on becoming the fastest hands of south of the Han River.

36:13.260 --> 36:14.470
Why are you against using blood pressure drugs

36:14.470 --> 36:15.640
from Cosmo

36:15.640 --> 36:16.710
Pharmaceuticals?

36:16.710 --> 36:18.100
The current ones are cheaper and better.

36:18.100 --> 36:19.700
Why use more expensive ones instead?

36:19.700 --> 36:21.490
Just do it.

36:21.490 --> 36:23.580
The company executive is Professor Park's cousin

36:23.580 --> 36:24.630
and the head surgeon's son-in-law,

36:24.630 --> 36:25.800
and your aunt's husband.

36:26.240 --> 36:27.060
So,

36:27.060 --> 36:28.480
This deal would benefit everyone.

36:28.480 --> 36:30.850
You're writing a clinical trial report on this case.

36:30.850 --> 36:33.340
Why do you do things that you'll get blamed for?

36:33.340 --> 36:34.390
Who's blaming me?

36:34.390 --> 36:35.410
Me.

36:35.410 --> 36:36.820
Do you pay for the drugs?

36:36.820 --> 36:38.680
If you want to become Albert Schweitzer,

36:38.680 --> 36:40.110
do some volunteer work.

36:40.110 --> 36:41.360
They don't have enough doctors in Africa,

36:41.360 --> 36:42.850
so someone dies every three seconds.

36:42.850 --> 36:45.430
Hurry up if you want to save the earth.

36:45.430 --> 36:46.300
Due to your incompetence,

36:46.300 --> 36:47.410
you misdiagnose

36:47.410 --> 36:49.550
three out of four patients.

36:49.550 --> 36:51.300
Why don't you get yourself a good lawyer

36:51.300 --> 36:52.760
to keep your license?

36:52.760 --> 36:53.860
Hey!

36:55.160 --> 36:56.170
Go away.

36:56.170 --> 36:57.770
I want to finish my lunch in peace.

36:58.570 --> 36:59.770
Cheers!

37:05.360 --> 37:06.160
Yum!

37:07.810 --> 37:09.150
Drink it slowly.

37:09.150 --> 37:10.980
Why? It's so yummy.

37:10.980 --> 37:12.860
Go home tonight.

37:14.300 --> 37:15.460
You haven't gone home for days

37:15.460 --> 37:16.680
which made the interns a hard time.

37:16.680 --> 37:18.250
Are they complaining?

37:19.260 --> 37:20.440
I haven't thought about that.

37:22.310 --> 37:23.630
I have surgery tomorrow morning.

37:23.630 --> 37:25.050
Don't perform surgeries anymore.

37:26.420 --> 37:29.020
I'm the sexiest in the OR.

37:36.430 --> 37:37.460
What?

37:37.960 --> 37:41.510
It just reminded me of something.

37:41.510 --> 37:42.840
What?

37:47.690 --> 37:49.620
This and that.

37:52.390 --> 37:58.190
Mineral water. Wine. Candles.

37:59.490 --> 38:03.260
X-ray pictures. Hair bands.

38:06.390 --> 38:07.590
I'm going crazy here.

38:09.120 --> 38:10.420
Why are you laughing?

38:10.750 --> 38:11.670
Have you gone crazy?

38:12.540 --> 38:14.450
I thought I was okay.

38:17.440 --> 38:19.130
It's killing me, Ji Soo.

38:25.540 --> 38:26.360
Can I give you a hug?

38:28.840 --> 38:29.780
No.

38:30.370 --> 38:31.150
More wine?

38:32.670 --> 38:33.590
Sure.

38:39.020 --> 38:41.120
Go ahead and drink up.

38:56.630 --> 38:57.630
Sir!

38:57.630 --> 38:58.910
Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo was ordered to transfer

38:58.910 --> 39:00.310
to Company Mouru in the Taebaek Unit in Uruk

39:00.310 --> 39:03.370
as a member of the medical team on November 30th, 2015.

39:03.370 --> 39:06.500
Therefore, I'm reporting to you. Sir!

39:09.870 --> 39:11.160
Good luck

39:11.980 --> 39:13.320
and don't get sick this time.

39:13.320 --> 39:14.980
I'm sorry to have worried you.

39:16.050 --> 39:17.390
Please take care of yourself.

39:18.420 --> 39:19.160
I will.

39:19.160 --> 39:20.810
Thank you for your fair order.

39:20.810 --> 39:21.790
Thanks.

39:21.790 --> 39:26.590
I was only unfair to him.

39:27.120 --> 39:29.480
Because of that, I made my daughter miserable.

39:29.480 --> 39:31.800
My plan was a complete failure.

39:32.690 --> 39:35.870
I know you only think about him

39:38.260 --> 39:40.170
but I only think about you.

39:41.660 --> 39:43.910
While thinking about him,

39:43.910 --> 39:46.440
think about me who's worried about his own daughter.

39:46.860 --> 39:48.300
While you're at it,

39:48.670 --> 39:50.030
forgive me

39:51.760 --> 39:53.210
if you can.

40:06.090 --> 40:08.330
Isn't it too early to drink?

40:09.390 --> 40:11.220
I'm trying to adjust myself

40:11.220 --> 40:12.520
to Uruk time.

40:15.280 --> 40:16.800
I'm going back there.

40:18.810 --> 40:20.390
I'm jealous. I love Uruk.

40:20.390 --> 40:21.660
Do you want to come with me?

40:22.100 --> 40:23.120
Should I?

40:23.850 --> 40:25.630
They left together.

40:25.940 --> 40:27.450
We can go there together.

40:28.470 --> 40:29.940
You're silly.

40:34.950 --> 40:37.160
This is my farewell gift to you.

40:37.810 --> 40:39.190
I got them from their barracks.

40:41.120 --> 40:43.680
This is Sergeant Seo's girlfriend.

40:46.080 --> 40:48.580
That is Captain Yoo's fellow soldier.

40:53.840 --> 40:54.870
She's ugly.

40:55.700 --> 40:57.120
You win, Myung Joo.

41:00.100 --> 41:01.350
When are you leaving?

41:02.360 --> 41:03.840
Early Monday morning.

41:04.800 --> 41:06.930
I have three days.

41:07.310 --> 41:08.600
Drink for three days in a row?

41:09.980 --> 41:10.990
Are you in?

41:10.990 --> 41:12.920
I'm in.

41:24.850 --> 41:26.380
Recently,

41:27.490 --> 41:29.310
I remember sweet things that he did for me.

41:29.310 --> 41:31.300
I remember being mean to him.

41:34.180 --> 41:37.220
By the way, Captain Yoo and Sergeant Seo...

41:37.380 --> 41:39.220
How did the two start?

41:40.100 --> 41:42.200
I've always wondered  how they became friends.

41:42.200 --> 41:43.550
I’ve forgotten to ask

41:44.770 --> 41:46.260
and now no one to ask.

41:46.260 --> 41:47.430
I know.

41:48.610 --> 41:53.150
They first met because of a woman.

41:54.440 --> 41:55.980
A woman?

42:02.470 --> 42:03.780
I don’t know,

42:04.710 --> 42:06.850
but it feels weird.

42:08.830 --> 42:10.850
I did my part.

42:10.850 --> 42:11.890
Don't forget to tell Captain Yoo Shi Jin

42:11.930 --> 42:15.050
that we're dating.

42:45.690 --> 42:46.780
I'm your captain.

42:47.280 --> 42:48.470
Can I share your umbrella?

42:49.320 --> 42:50.440
We're dating.

42:52.990 --> 42:54.590
Are we?

42:57.130 --> 42:59.220
I'm dating Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo.

43:06.590 --> 43:08.470
I'm dating Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo.

43:09.370 --> 43:11.700
How long have you been dating her?

43:11.700 --> 43:12.960
It's been a year.

43:13.710 --> 43:17.230
When did you first meet her?

43:17.230 --> 43:19.210
A month ago during the 400-kilometer walk.

43:21.520 --> 43:23.580
Yet you've been dating her for a year?

43:25.400 --> 43:26.980
I can assure you

43:27.370 --> 43:29.390
that I'm dating Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo.

43:30.550 --> 43:33.690
Do you know Myung Joo's father's a three-star?

43:37.220 --> 43:38.630
Anyone can make

43:38.630 --> 43:41.400
three mistakes in his or her life.

43:41.820 --> 43:43.230
Her father's criminal record

43:43.230 --> 43:45.270
can't be an obstacle to our love.

43:46.190 --> 43:48.050
Like I said,

43:48.050 --> 43:49.950
I'm dating Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo.

43:52.470 --> 43:53.990
I hope you do.

43:53.990 --> 43:54.980
I will.

43:57.770 --> 43:59.040
It's been a year.

43:59.200 --> 44:00.080
Yeah, yeah.

44:00.410 --> 44:01.380
I'm so jealous.

44:03.740 --> 44:04.790
Are you giving up on her?

44:06.980 --> 44:08.380
I hope I can find a woman whom I met a month ago

44:08.380 --> 44:11.350
and have been dating for a year.

44:13.370 --> 44:16.030
You and I won't be fighting over Myung Joo.

44:18.160 --> 44:19.950
Let's be on the same team

44:20.590 --> 44:22.450
when we fight.

44:31.410 --> 44:33.040
I love drinking in the daytime.

44:41.170 --> 44:42.210
You know what?

44:42.700 --> 44:44.600
We've never said "I love you" to each other.

44:45.350 --> 44:46.770
We have, with gestures.

44:48.660 --> 44:50.890
We've never said "I love you" to each other

44:50.890 --> 44:52.730
but we held hands and kissed.

44:53.410 --> 44:55.160
Wow! We're saucy.

44:55.160 --> 44:56.480
Is there anything you can't say?

44:56.480 --> 44:57.950
There's something I couldn't say.

44:58.150 --> 44:59.590
Why don't you say it now?

45:00.280 --> 45:02.690
Let's go in alphabetical order.

45:02.690 --> 45:04.200
"K" comes before "Y," so you go first, Dr. Kang.

45:04.200 --> 45:05.810
If you want to hear it, say it first.

45:06.280 --> 45:07.740
Ladies first.

45:08.940 --> 45:10.140
Or seniors first?

45:10.680 --> 45:12.220
Why are you asking me to say it first?

45:12.220 --> 45:13.430
You haven't said it to me yet.

45:13.430 --> 45:14.460
I love you.

45:14.460 --> 45:15.810
Geeze!

45:17.120 --> 45:18.400
I love you.

45:20.590 --> 45:22.130
Copy that!

45:23.990 --> 45:25.410
I love you too.

45:25.410 --> 45:28.090
I'll devote my body and mind to you.

45:28.730 --> 45:29.580
Okay.

45:30.710 --> 45:31.800
Do you swear?

45:32.170 --> 45:33.120
Yes.

45:34.170 --> 45:35.240
Cheers!

45:37.710 --> 45:38.610
Do you put it in here?

45:39.270 --> 45:41.160
It excites me a little.

45:42.650 --> 45:45.330
Geeze! It's still too early in the evening.

46:03.500 --> 46:05.250
How do I look?

46:06.480 --> 46:08.730
Am I pretty with the light behind me?

46:18.760 --> 46:20.550
You're pretty all the time.

46:41.950 --> 46:43.300
I missed you.

46:43.900 --> 46:45.280
Me too.

46:45.580 --> 46:49.800
Then why didn't you come back?

46:50.120 --> 46:51.860
I was busy keeping peace.

46:52.760 --> 46:54.830
What about the promises

46:56.330 --> 46:57.870
that you made to me?

46:58.180 --> 46:59.650
Did they mean nothing to you?

46:59.650 --> 47:01.170
I was trying to come back.

47:04.000 --> 47:05.770
I did everything to come back to you.

47:08.440 --> 47:10.340
But you didn't come back.

47:12.240 --> 47:13.640
You didn't.

47:17.670 --> 47:19.120
I won't read it.

48:32.300 --> 48:33.740
I won't read it

48:35.070 --> 48:37.050
until I die.

48:40.120 --> 48:41.960
I won't give you the satisfaction.

48:45.890 --> 48:47.720
I've checked my baggage and am walking to the gate now.

48:50.900 --> 48:52.500
No. I'll stop over at Abu Dhabi

48:52.500 --> 48:53.830
and arrive in Albania.

48:54.660 --> 48:56.650
It's a long way to go.

48:57.250 --> 48:58.720
Hey, I'm getting another phone call.

48:59.570 --> 49:02.470
-I'll call you when I get there.
-Okay.

49:02.870 --> 49:04.280
Hello?

49:06.220 --> 49:07.490
Daniel?

49:09.420 --> 49:10.700
When did you come?

49:11.060 --> 49:13.450
By the way, what are you doing here?

49:13.450 --> 49:14.470
What's all this?

49:14.470 --> 49:17.060
I'm here to protest the FTA meeting

49:17.060 --> 49:18.740
but they won't let me enter the country.

49:19.250 --> 49:21.050
I'm okay as long as I stay behind this line.

49:21.050 --> 49:23.340
I'm going to start a one-man protest right here.

49:24.610 --> 49:25.720
Awesome!

49:26.150 --> 49:27.090
I'm an international criminal

49:27.090 --> 49:29.570
who's banned from 12 countries.

49:29.730 --> 49:32.060
Girls tend to fall for bad guys.

49:32.660 --> 49:34.420
Are you on vacation?

49:34.420 --> 49:35.280
Volunteer work.

49:35.280 --> 49:37.820
Right. The Albanian refugee camp.

49:37.820 --> 49:40.140
I heard it from Dr. Lee Chi Hoon.

49:40.140 --> 49:41.600
Volunteer work

49:41.600 --> 49:43.020
is kind of addictive.

49:43.840 --> 49:45.250
I'm doing it

49:45.250 --> 49:46.250
for personal reasons.

49:47.120 --> 49:48.760
Tomorrow is the anniversary of his death.

49:49.090 --> 49:50.220
I'm going back there to remember him.

50:14.560 --> 50:16.340
From polio and tuberculosis

50:16.340 --> 50:17.450
to AIDS,

50:17.450 --> 50:19.720
which were considered as incurable diseases,

50:19.720 --> 50:23.450
many of these have been conquered by the improvements of medicines.

50:23.450 --> 50:26.110
However, 14 million people are still dying

50:26.110 --> 50:27.390
due to medicines,

50:27.390 --> 50:29.170
not diseases.

50:30.210 --> 50:32.910
I saw Daniel at the airport.

50:32.910 --> 50:34.260
It was so weird.

50:35.630 --> 50:37.400
By the way, my blood type is O positive.

50:37.890 --> 50:39.510
I just wanted to let you know

50:39.900 --> 50:41.520
that I'm not a doll, but a human.

50:43.110 --> 50:45.960
I heard there's a desert around here.

50:47.060 --> 50:48.680
Will there be an oasis as well?

50:49.850 --> 50:51.720
"You can't patent the sun."

50:52.090 --> 50:54.140
That's what Dr. Salk,

50:54.140 --> 50:55.120
who developed the polio vaccine, said.

50:55.120 --> 50:58.520
You've been advocating that the patent for essential vaccines should be abolished.

50:58.520 --> 50:59.960
But for companies,

50:59.960 --> 51:01.980
to develop new medicines aren't patents essential?

51:01.980 --> 51:03.840
Multinational pharmaceutical companies use

51:03.840 --> 51:05.420
the majority of their profits for marketing.

51:05.420 --> 51:08.460
If they weaponize epidemic vaccines to make money,

51:08.460 --> 51:11.440
pharmaceutical companies are no better than drug cartels.

51:11.840 --> 51:13.870
This is what Nelson Mandela said.

51:13.870 --> 51:16.120
"People Not Profit!"

51:16.450 --> 51:17.280
You should never

51:17.280 --> 51:20.450
replace human life for profit.

51:23.430 --> 51:25.040
I'm this kind of doctor now.

51:25.960 --> 51:29.660
Are you proud of me looking down from up there?

51:33.480 --> 51:35.110
I'll check again after a week.

51:35.110 --> 51:36.710
Try not to use your wrist for a week.

51:37.750 --> 51:39.520
Yes, ma'am.

51:41.700 --> 51:42.630
Deputy captain,

51:43.000 --> 51:44.320
don't make him work.

51:48.830 --> 51:49.970
Yes, ma'am.

51:53.360 --> 51:54.500
By the way, aren't you eating lunch?

51:55.150 --> 51:57.170
I can cook the best ramen in the world.

52:02.340 --> 52:03.980
Why did you come back here?

52:03.980 --> 52:05.370
Sergeant Kim Ki Bum!

52:06.930 --> 52:08.220
I think I feel at home in the army.

52:13.670 --> 52:15.810
Sergeant Seo used to eat ramen a lot.

52:17.420 --> 52:18.770
Yes,

52:18.770 --> 52:20.170
he did.

52:22.420 --> 52:24.820
Go ahead and eat. It's good.

52:29.660 --> 52:30.990
You know what?

52:31.380 --> 52:32.600
It's snowing outside.

52:34.030 --> 52:34.670
Really?

52:35.500 --> 52:37.280
This is weird.

52:37.280 --> 52:39.290
It won’t snow in Uruk.

53:30.580 --> 53:32.130
I can do it.

53:35.030 --> 53:37.490
When you're in a relationship,

53:37.490 --> 53:38.900
your boyfriend usually does things that you can do yourself.

54:14.400 --> 54:16.200
Do you always risk

54:16.570 --> 54:18.920
your life

54:20.230 --> 54:21.720
in everything you do?

54:22.730 --> 54:25.010
I'm good at what I do.

54:25.010 --> 54:27.270
Not dying is one of them.

54:31.390 --> 54:33.390
Liar!

54:35.010 --> 54:36.480
I won't get hurt.

54:37.490 --> 54:38.990
I won't die.

54:41.730 --> 54:44.520
I'll come back. I promise.

54:49.680 --> 54:53.840
Liar! Enough!

54:55.540 --> 54:56.860
I love you.

54:59.020 --> 55:00.430
Please.

55:01.580 --> 55:03.300
I don't believe it.

55:13.230 --> 55:15.400
This is headquarters!

55:15.400 --> 55:17.990
Beauty! Please come in!

55:17.990 --> 55:21.180
Please bring some lidocaine on your way back.

55:24.660 --> 55:26.270
This is Beauty.

55:26.270 --> 55:28.210
Be there soon. Over.

55:52.730 --> 55:54.930
Stay here.

55:56.770 --> 55:57.900
This is Big Boss.

56:21.790 --> 56:25.270
Geeze. Now I'm hearing things.

56:35.360 --> 56:36.580
This is Big Boss!

56:59.440 --> 57:02.660
Beauty! Please turn around. Over!

57:28.880 --> 57:30.710
It’s impossible!

57:40.710 --> 57:43.890
It’s impossible!

57:44.330 --> 57:45.970
I can’t believe it!

58:22.840 --> 58:24.710
It's been forever.

58:28.570 --> 58:30.260
Were you...

58:32.330 --> 58:34.980
Were you alive?

58:36.350 --> 58:37.570
I pull off such difficult

58:39.400 --> 58:40.860
tasks all the time.

58:53.130 --> 58:54.870
You're alive.

58:57.960 --> 58:59.980
You're alive.

59:01.420 --> 59:02.340
I'm sorry.

59:05.980 --> 59:07.170
I'm so sorry.
